= Ghaki Logger - Fancy logging

Ghaki Logger is a collection of extensions for the core Logger object.

== Download

The latest version of Ghaki Logger can be found at

* git@github.com:ghaki/ghaki-logger.git

== Installation

The preferred method of installing Ghaki Logger is through its GEM file.

  % [sudo] gem install ghaki-logger-1.0.0.gem

